title: Grateful Dead Live at Red Rocks Amphitheatre on 1984-06-12
taper: Executive Crew Tom Pinney, Sean Murtha, Chris Kidwell, Kyle Holbrook
description:
Set I
Alabama Getaway >
Greatest Story Ever Told
Friend Of The Devil
Little Red Rooster
Big Railroad Blues
Me & My Uncle >
Mexicali Blues
Althea
Looks Like Rain
Might As Well
Set II
Scarlet Begonias >
Touch Of Grey >
Estimated Prophet >
Eyes Of The World >
Drums >
Space >
The Other One >
Wharf Rat >
Around & Around >
Johnny B. Goode

Encore:
U.S. Blues


Comment
Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Brent Mydland - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
